ion (and got it more right than the media and pollsters). The idea that the=
re are no use cases is dead. Now, the question is how many really great pro=
ducts will be built this cycle. </p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: r=
gb(54, 55, 55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;"><span>As I wrote in </sp=
